import Page from './main'
import img1 from '../assets/img1.png'
import img2 from '../assets/img2.png'
import img3 from '../assets/img3.png'
import NavBar from './NavBar'
function App() {
    return (
        <>
        
            <Page 
                img = {img1}
                name = 'Japan'
            />
            <Page
                img = {img2}
                name = 'America'
            />
            <Page
                img = {img3}
                name = 'France'
             />
        </>
    )
}

export default App
